dict.string: This is a quick tutorial;before you start shooting!
Buns try to protect Burgers..;Drop them first!
Catch a carrot with your plate; You will move faster for some time!
Drop the ingredients;and destroy the Burgers!
An Apple in your plate;doubles your hitting power.
Apples and Carrots together?;No one can stop you!
Use any number of moves;but finish in time!
Soda glasses block your way.;But you only have to destroy Burgers.
Catch Water bottles;and you will destroy Soda!
Water and Carrot?;Will destroy Soda fast!
Healthy food?;Will help you destroy enemies!
Sticky Ketchup will stop you;to protect their boss!
Real tomatoe will destroy;red sticky obstacles
Use any number of moves;but finish in time!
Touch Fries...;and you will end up with 2 Fries
Make sure you catch Cucumber;before Carrots!
Carrots may let you touch;more Fries!
Avoid all allies;and shoot your enemy
Put Pea in your plate;And shoot all obstacles
Healthy food is here to help!
Too many Carrot?; May be too Fast!!
Lemon for Mustard;and Carrots for speed!
Carrots may let you touch;dangerous Mustard!
Use Lemon to destroy Mustard;then drop Burgers!
Avoid all allies;and shoot your enemy
About to touch Mustard?;Tap anywhere to stop your plate
Tap the healthy icon;to get Powerups!
Use the correct Powerup!;One at a time
